channel.title: Small portforward problem!
channel.description:
Dear, moparscape!
I have a small problem, When i go to my router page-> 192.168.0.2 I click advanced,then i click Virtual Servers, but when i click it, My internet goes down. (So i can't go back on internet for 30 minutes.) [IMG]http://i361.photobucket.com/albums/oo51/JoeySarii/help.jpg[/img] Is there any way to fix it, Thanks, I D D S I
